#: ../../source/inventories.rst:506
msgid "**Overwrite**: If checked, any hosts and groups that were previously present on the external source but are now removed, will be removed from the controller inventory. Hosts and groups that were not managed by the inventory source will be promoted to the next manually created group, or if there is no manually created group to promote them into, they will be left in the \"all\" default group for the inventory."
